      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it runs smoothly with a healthy engine and responsive transmission, and all scheduled maintenance is up to date. The exterior presents well, though you will find some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches from normal use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, showing only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster and floor mats. It is a dependable car that offers a great balance of quality and value.",
