    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved and consistently maintained, so it\u2019s totally ready for all your upcoming adventures! If you\u2019re looking for a reliable set of wheels that still looks great pulling into the driveway, this is the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
