    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a stellar example of pride in ownership, offering a harmonious blend of performance and comfort. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the front fascia\u2014honest evidence of highway miles. The alloy wheels are free of curb rash and are wrapped in tires with significant tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the smoke-free interior features supple leather seating with only minimal softening on the driver\u2019s bolster. All technological amenities, including the intuitive infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine idling is whisper-quiet, and the transmission provides crisp, confident shifts. We have kept a comprehensive folder of service records, including a recent oil change and a thorough multi-point inspection, ensuring this car is ready for the road from day one. It delivers a composed, rattle-free ride that reflects its careful upkeep.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
