    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my awesome car! It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in really solid shape. It\u2019s super clean, runs great, and is totally ready for its next adventure. I\u2019ve truly loved driving this, and I know you will too! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
