    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis remains taut with a factory-spec limited-slip differential providing excellent lateral grip. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high torque loads. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its age, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain razor-sharp. It\u2019s a driver-focused machine with a pristine power-to-weight ratio, ready for the apex.",
